full_title: Chk Chk Boom by Stray Kids
title: Chk Chk Boom

description.plain:
Stray Kids are feeling more confident than ever on their comeback single “Chk Chk Boom,” the title track of July 2024’s ATE. Staying true to their music style, the track consists of an energizing, electronic dance-pop instrumental, with lyrics that threaten their enemies to keep far and strive to achieve higher than just their goals.

In conjunction with being featured on the Deadpool & Wolverine soundtrack with their single “Slash”, the music video features the lead actors, Ryan Reynolds and Hugh Jackman, as news reporters and their roles from the Deadpool & Wolverine series. Additionally, the rest of the video features disastrous and fun scenes of the group in New York.
